  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add pitted dates and sauté for 2-3 minutes, until they start to soften.",
    "Add penne rigate pasta and toss to coat with the date mixture.",
    "Pour in chilled coconut cream and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and let cook for 2-3 minutes, until the sauce thickens.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot."
  ],
